  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   0.898665655534571         24.4539           563.92          2359.45
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.552650772118640        -15.0384          -346.79         -1450.98
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.193379143044502         -5.2621          -121.35          -507.72
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.048860039873192          1.3295            30.66           128.28
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.027972698670175         -0.7612           -17.55           -73.44
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.173523081574446          4.7218           108.89           455.58
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

